6y.title: Pivotal achievement
6y.text:
Clickbait: Which types of AIs, if they work, will upset the current gameboard and make a large difference 200 million years later?

# Examples.

Some forms of [Limited AI](limited_AI-1) are so limited as to be of questionable relevance within [the larger dilemma](ValueAchievementDilemma-1).

A [central example](central example-1) is a heavily [Boxed](ai_boxing-2) [Oracle](oracle-1) that [can only tell us whether certain theorems are provable in Zermelo-Fraenkel set theory](zf_provability_oracle-1).  While this Oracle may indeed have been so heavily Boxed as to be genuinely safe, nobody knows how to save the world using a trustworthy means of knowing that certain theorems are provable in ZF.
